comments: Hood (POR) makes marginal contact to Curry's (GSW) body as Curry receives the pass.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Covington's (POR) path during the pick and absorbs the contact.
As Covington (POR) contests Curry's (GSW) put-back shot attempt, incidental contact occurs after Curry's release.
As Hood (POR) retrieves the rebound, marginal arm contact occurs with Toscano-Anderson (GSW).
Bazemore's (GSW) hand brushes Lillard (POR) during his dribble, and the contact is marginal. The whistled contact from Bazemore to Lillard occurs prior to any ensuing contact from Wiggins (GSW).
Anthony (POR) makes marginal contact to Curry's (GSW) arm as he starts his dribble on the perimeter.
Covington (POR) makes incidental contact to Bazemore (GSW) during his pass attempt.
Trent Jr. (POR) briefly grasps and releases Toscano-Anderson's (GSW) shorts during the rebound, and the contact is marginal.
Bazemore (GSW) brushes Lillard's (POR) body as Lillard is already losing control of the ball on the perimeter.
Hood (POR) is established in Curry's (GSW) path when marginal contact occurs during the drive.
Green (GSW) commits a take foul on Covington (POR).

Replay review of the foul called on Green (GSW) pursuant to a coach?s challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Lillard (POR) is established in Green's path and absorbs the body contact in the chest during Green's driving shot attempt.
